27
00:02:00,870 --> 00:02:04,620
<font size="46"><b>It's too embarrassing to read it myself so I'd like Ikuchan to read it.</b></font>

28
00:02:04,620 --> 00:02:05,580
<font size="46"><b>- Okay!</b></font>

29
00:02:05,580 --> 00:02:09,620
<font size="46"><b>Uwah! Such an important thing...</b></font>

30
00:02:10,040 --> 00:02:11,330
<font size="46"><b>Dear Kazumi,</b></font>

31
00:02:11,330 --> 00:02:15,620
<font size="46"><b>The hardest work bears fruit, 
