32
00:02:15,620 --> 00:02:21,330
<font size="46"><b>You're working in the entertainment world which everybody admires.</b></font>

33
00:02:21,330 --> 00:02:25,940
<font size="46"><b>I'm very proud to have a daughter like you.</b></font>

34
00:02:25,940 --> 00:02:28,640
<font size="46"><b>It's finally time for you to become independent...</b></font>

35
00:02:28,640 --> 00:02:33,110
<font size="46"><b>To me, your presence is huge.</b></font>

36
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:36,750
<font size="46"><b>Thank you for always being with me.</b></font>

37
00:02:37,090 --> 00:02:39,170
<font size="46"><b>I will work hard too.</b></font>

38
00:02:39,530 --> 00:02:43,200
<font size="46"><b>I'll always pray for your success and happiness.</b></font>

39
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:46,060
<font size="46"><b>I'll always be watching over you.</b></font>

40
00:02:46,060 --> 00:02:47,570
<font size="46"><b>Please rely on me.</b></font>

41
