<font size="46"><b>You live at home, right?</b></font>

50
00:03:03,570 --> 00:03:06,430
<font size="46"><b>She isn't separated, but just the topic...</b></font>

51
00:03:06,430 --> 00:03:08,920
<font size="46"><b>I would be so happy...</b></font>

52
00:03:08,920 --> 00:03:13,360
<font size="46"><b>Y-yeah! When I moved I was really upset but...</b></font>

53
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:16,790
<font size="46"><b>I have this... and I look at it when it gets hard.</b></font>

54
00:03:16,790 --> 00:03:20,920
<font size="46"><b>That's something to be happy about.</b></font>

55
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:26,150
<font size="46"><b>But... but, like... how to say it... 
Well, people who are living with their families</b></font>

56
00:03:26,150 --> 00:03:30,690
