59
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:40,390
<font size="46"><b>or even "that's good." They always said "have fun."</b></font>

60
00:03:40,390 --> 00:03:42,390
<font size="46"><b>Ah!</b></font>

61
00:03:42,390 --> 00:03:44,000
<font size="46"><b>She didn't say either.</b></font>

62
00:03:44,020 --> 00:03:46,020
<font size="46"><b>Anything is fine, just have fun!</b></font>

63
00:03:46,020 --> 00:03:48,090
<font size="46"><b>Ah! That's nice!</b></font>

64
00:03:48,090 --> 00:03:50,090
<font size="46"><b>And that has always helped me.</b></font>

65
00:03:50,220 --> 00:03:52,090
<font size="46"><b>Wow, that's so nice...</b></font>

66
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:55,440
<font size="46"><b>I'm happy about something they avoid saying...</b></font>

67
00:03:55,440 --> 00:04:02,200
<font size="46"><b>When we were doing principal, it was really rough and I often say "I wanna go back to Osaka!"</b></font>

68
00:04:02,340 --> 00:04:08,280
<font size="46"><b>My mom came all the way to Tokyo, 
 she was crying a lot when she saw me cry.</b></font>

69
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:11,040
<font size="46"><b>It was the first time I saw my mom cry</b></font>

70
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:14,830
<font size="46"><b>but she never said "come on back to Osaka."</b></font>

71
00:04:14,830 --> 00:04:18,190
<font size="46"><b>She just told me "do you best here" while crying...</b></font>

72
00:04:18,190 --> 00:04:21,280
<font size="46"><b>and that was... ah, even now when I think about it...</b></font>

73
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:25,210
<font size="46"><b>Back then, my mom had it rough but...</b></font>

74
00:04:25,210 --> 00:04:29,170
<font size="46"><b>she was still supporting me. That made me very happy.</b></font>

75
00:04:29,840 --> 00:04:32,260
<font size="46"><b>People who came to Tokyo, how was it?</b></font>

76
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:34,260
<font size="46"><b>Lonely...</b></font>

77
00:04:34,260 --> 00:04:38,580
<font size="46"><b>I thought so many times I want to go home, but I have a dream...</b></font>

78
00:04:38,580 --> 00:04:43,180
<font size="46"><b>That's why I came here. I feel like I can't go back until it comes true.</b></font>

79
00:04:43,180 --> 00:04:43,830
<font size="46"><b>I understand!</b></font>

80
00:04:43,830 --> 00:04:46,690
<font size="46"><b>I came to Tokyo before I met everyone</b></font>

81
00:04:46,690 --> 00:04:50,410
<font size="46"><b>so I felt less lonely after I met everyone.</b></font>

82
00:04:51,460 --> 00:04:53,520
<font size="46"><b>Until then I was always alone...</b></font>

83
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:55,520
<font size="46"><b>I see...</b></font>

84
