163
00:09:27,780 --> 00:09:29,270
<font size="46"><b>Ah.. I wonder...</b></font>

164
00:09:29,270 --> 00:09:32,760
<font size="46"><b>You're not unfashionable anymore. Look at this sharp looking necklace!</b></font>

165
00:09:32,760 --> 00:09:34,980
