166
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:39,620
<font size="46"><b>Matsui Rena-san joined recently, right?</b></font>

167
00:09:39,620 --> 00:09:42,410
<font size="46"><b>What was your first impression of her?</b></font>

168
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:45,050
