170
00:09:48,690 --> 00:09:54,050
<font size="46"><b>But of course, we weren't thinking that Rena-san would join us...</b></font>

171
00:09:54,050 --> 00:09:57,840
<font size="46"><b>When her concurrency began, we were all very nervous.</b></font>

172
00:09:57,840 --> 00:10:01,300
<font size="46"><b>But she eased our nervousness for us...</b></font>

173
00:10:01,300 --> 00:10:03,520
<font size="46"><b>And now we really fit together.</b></font>

